abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Yale defeats Harvard, 59-50; other scores noted.

headline.print_headline: Yale Sweeps Harvard to Hold League Lead Over Princeton
headline.main: Yale Sweeps Harvard to Hold League Lead Over Princeton

snippet: Shawn Craig’s attempt to weave through three defenders failed, costing the United Tribes Technical College a chance to try a 3-pointer that would have given them a 1-point road win.
